  15. BEGIN{FS="[,)] *";count=0};
  16. /DOMAIN_STATE/{
  17.   print "Store_" $2 " MACRO reg";
  18.   print "  mov [r14+" count "], reg";
  19.   print "ENDM";
  20.   print "Load_" $2 " MACRO reg";
  21.   print "  mov reg, [r14+" count "]";
  22.   print  "ENDM";
  23.   print "Push_" $2 " MACRO";
  24.   print "  push [r14+" count "]";
  25.   print "ENDM";
  26.   print "Pop_" $2 " MACRO";
  27.   print "  pop [r14+" count "]";
  28.   print "ENDM";
  29.   print "Cmp_" $2 " MACRO reg";
  30.   print "  cmp reg, [r14+" count "]";
  31.   print "ENDM";
  32.   count+=8
  33. }
